column1: query
SELECT apid FROM airports WHERE apid >= 60 ORDER BY apid ASC LIMIT 10

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT airlines.iata), airports.country, airports.iata, airlines.active FROM routes JOIN airlines ON routes.alid = airlines.alid JOIN airports ON routes.dst_apid = airports.apid WHERE airlines.alid != 49 GROUP BY airlines.active, airports.country, airports.iata
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT g.airline), g.dst_apid, g.rid, g.src_apid FROM routes AS g WHERE g.rid >= 83 GROUP BY g.dst_apid, g.rid, g.src_apid;
SELECT icao, country, iata FROM airlines WHERE alid BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR alid >= 60 LIMIT 6;
SELECT e.alid FROM airlines AS e WHERE  e.alid >= 47 LIMIT 4
SELECT MIN(e.elevation), MIN(e.x), e.country FROM airports AS e WHERE e.x > 17 GROUP BY e.country HAVING MIN(e.x) > 71 LIMIT 4
SELECT elevation FROM airports WHERE  y = 72 ORDER BY elevation ASC LIMIT 4
SELECT COUNT(elevation), icao FROM airports WHERE  y != 41 ORDER BY icao ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT src_apid), rid, alid FROM routes WHERE dst_apid >= 97 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM airports AS s WHERE s.apid < 1 AND routes.src_apid = s.apid LIMIT 7) ORDER BY alid ASC
SELECT MIN(s.dst_apid), MIN(s.src_apid), s.codeshare FROM routes AS s WHERE s.dst_apid BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY s.codeshare DESC LIMIT 4
SELECT elevation, x FROM airports WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM routes AS w WHERE  w.dst_apid = 96 AND airports.apid = w.dst_apid) ORDER BY elevation DESC
SELECT x FROM airports WHERE  elevation != 91 ORDER BY x DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT a.airline, a.dst_ap FROM routes AS a WHERE  a.alid = 35 LIMIT 7
SELECT f.name FROM airlines AS f WHERE  f.alid > 84
SELECT T2.dst_apid, T2.codeshare FROM airlines AS T1 JOIN routes AS T2 ON T1.alid = T2.alid
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o.name), o.icao FROM airports AS o WHERE o.y = 74 GROUP BY o.icao HAVING SUM(o.elevation) <= 4
SELECT AVG(alid), dst_ap FROM routes GROUP BY dst_ap
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT j.active), j.iata FROM airlines AS j WHERE j.active > (SELECT MIN(active) FROM airlines AS u) LIMIT 1

SELECT COUNT(airlines.alid), COUNT(routes.apid), AVG(routes.src_apid) FROM routes JOIN airlines ON routes.alid = airlines.alid JOIN airports ON routes.dst_apid = airports.apid WHERE  routes.src_apid < 53
SELECT AVG(y), name FROM airports WHERE  elevation <= 80 GROUP BY name LIMIT 2
SELECT rid, airports.iata FROM routes JOIN airports ON routes.dst_apid = airports.apid JOIN airlines ON airlines.alid = routes.alid WHERE rid < 44 ORDER BY airports.iata ASC LIMIT 9
SELECT MIN(p.alid), p.icao, p.callsign FROM airlines AS p WHERE p.alid BETWEEN 1 AND 10;

SELECT airlines.alid, routes.src_ap FROM routes JOIN airports ON routes.dst_apid = airports.apid JOIN airlines ON routes.alid = airlines.alid WHERE airports.y BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY routes.src_ap HAVING MIN(routes.rid) <= 86 ORDER BY airlines.alid ASC;
SELECT rid FROM routes WHERE  rid < 92 ORDER BY rid ASC
SELECT AVG(u.rid) FROM routes AS u WHERE u.dst_apid != 55;
SELECT o.x FROM airports AS o WHERE o.apid BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR o.apid <= 100

SELECT l.name, l.iata FROM airports AS l JOIN routes AS r ON l.apid = r.dst_apid WHERE l.elevation BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM routes AS i WHERE l.apid = i.dst_apid LIMIT 4) GROUP BY l.iata HAVING MAX(l.elevation) <= 95
SELECT src_apid, alid FROM routes WHERE src_apid <= 72 GROUP BY alid;
SELECT l.codeshare FROM routes AS l WHERE  l.alid >= 18 ORDER BY l.codeshare ASC
SELECT routes.alid FROM routes JOIN airlines ON routes.alid = airlines.alid WHERE  src_apid = 82 ORDER BY routes.alid DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T2.country), T2.apid FROM routes AS T1 JOIN airports AS T2 ON T1.dst_apid = T2.apid WHERE T2.y = 63 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM airports AS T3 WHERE T3.x > 63 AND T3.apid = T1.src_apid) ORDER BY T2.apid ASC
SELECT airports.country, airports.name FROM airports AS m WHERE  airports.x > 54 ORDER BY airports.country ASC

SELECT MAX(airports.x), u.x FROM airports JOIN airports AS u ON airports.apid = u.apid WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM routes WHERE dst_apid BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND alid > 10 AND airports.apid = src_apid) GROUP BY u.x ORDER BY u.x DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT r.src_apid), r.dst_apid, r.airline FROM routes r JOIN airports a ON r.dst_apid = a.apid WHERE r.dst_apid <= 98 GROUP BY r.dst_apid, r.airline;
SELECT r.alid, r.codeshare FROM routes r JOIN airports a ON r.dst_apid = a.apid WHERE a.y < 20 LIMIT 6;
